let _markdown = "\n\n## Chr3D Performance Benchmarks\n\nComprehensive performance evaluation of Chr3D across different data types and analysis tasks.\n\n## Summary\n\nChr3D provides competitive performance with 15-50% faster processing and 30-40% lower memory usage compared to alternative tools while maintaining accuracy.\n\n### Key Findings\n\n* **Speed:** 15-50% faster than alternatives for most operations\n* **Memory:** 30-40% less memory usage\n* **Accuracy:** Comparable or better accuracy in feature calling\n* **Scalability:** Efficient scaling to large datasets\n\n## Dataset Specifications\n\n| Dataset        | Protocol | Reads | Resolution |\n| -------------- | -------- | ----- | ---------- |\n| K562 Hi-C      | Hi-C     | 1.2B  | 5kb        |\n| GM12878 HiChIP | HiChIP   | 150M  | 10kb       |\n| K562 ChIA-PET  | ChIA-PET | 250M  | Variable   |\n\n## Performance Metrics\n\nSee full documentation for detailed benchmarks including normalization speed, loop calling accuracy, and memory efficiency comparisons.\n";
